@startuml contacts-state
' Context: contacts
' SDD: PROM-PERSONAL-CONTACTS, SYS-CONTACTS
' Revision: 2026-07-19

title Contacts — ContactsMachine

state Loading
state Ready

[*] --> Loading : LoadContacts

Loading --> Ready : ContactsLoaded
Loading --> Ready : ContactsLoadFailed

Ready --> Loading : LoadContacts\n[after CRUD]
Ready --> Ready : SetSearchQuery
Ready --> Ready : AddInternalContact
Ready --> Ready : AddExternalContact
Ready --> Ready : RemoveInternalContact

note right of Ready
  SearchProfiles is a command
  handled in UI sheet; results are
  local until AddInternalContact.
  List filter (SetSearchQuery) does
  not change machine state.
end note

@enduml
